[The Magic Valley is a region in south-central Idaho consisting of Blaine, Camas, Cassia, Gooding, Jerome, Lincoln, Minidoka and Twin Falls Counties (https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Magic_Valley). - Mod.ML]

