[Mubi North is a Local Government Area (LGA) of Adamawa State, Nigeria (https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mubi_North). A map showing the location of Mubi North can be found at https://www.google.com/maps/place/Mubi+North+Local+Government+Secretariat. - Mod.ML]

